Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that the water in the toilet
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,became bright red with blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:49.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure whether it was blood or not
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure that\Nthe water became bright red.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that I think of it .
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could have been red water caused
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by a rusty water pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:03.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there was a sharp acidy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,just a while ago. But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it was aired out
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because the door has been left open.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It may be so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It smells of
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:19.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:23.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just want to look more closely and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,share it with my classmates at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:31.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the ghost scared the great detective
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogoro Mori out, of his wits!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I aint leaving yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:39.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because ghosts don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, gee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A strange figure in the window was
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,just a reflection of someone among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bloody toilet water was
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:58.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,actually rusty water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This ominous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gloomy atmosphere\Njust lulled me to develop delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:07.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,what about the woman I saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really saw her on the TV screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A woman suffering serious burns, said,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:15.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go home. Go home
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just an illusion too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were no ghost programs listed on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:23.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the: TV: column of the newspaper either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, another likely explanation is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the resident of this room showed\Nus a spooky video
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in order to make us believe\Nthat this place is haunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:41.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:42.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I checked it out right away back-then.-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there was no tape In this VCR then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead, what I can't understand is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why we all fell asleep together back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that because of the curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:20:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone were to step onto\Nthis window rail.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like it would collapse easily
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:06.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The apartment building is
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,enclosed with high walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when I look out this window,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see the building under construction\Nbefore my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing with the window open?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bugs will fly in again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering\Nabout where of that building
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:24.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,gramps saw the death candle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was in the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,around the center of that building.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A red light was looming and moving
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,about in the sadly in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.09,0:21:37.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At times it turned a bluish white light too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do 3 this mean anyhow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We suddenly go faint,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then the apparition appears on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The toilet water suddenly turns red.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:55.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both can be explained scientifically,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:21:59.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I just can't understand the other two
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:04.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the death candle and the figure\Nby the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:09.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did the culprit do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the first place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,IS there really a culprit at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.59,0:22:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.86,0:22:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.63,0:22:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And for what reason is this being done?
