Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.92,0:23:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.33,0:23:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw not only red,\Nbut also a blue death candle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when I visited a room\Nwhere my senior was living.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.23,0:23:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if I turn off the light like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.94,0:24:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'believe nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.34,0:24:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that I can't comprehend scientifically
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.91,0:24:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I'm gonna unlock
